    
   Using the Automated Library Assistant, you can :

     - Check out an Item
     - Return an Item
     - Reserve an Item
     - Pay fines
     - View Transaction history
 

    How : On the library system's menu, click on My Account and choose 
    one of the displayed menu items.



    E-Mail - We will send you a courtesy e-mail when :

     - Reserved items are ready for pickup

    Note : You should have provided your e-mail (Gmail account) address during 
    membership registration. 



    Lost Item - In case of lost item :

     - A pre-defined price for the lost item(s) will be charged to your account.